{"tid":2347371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幸福賓周浩德 我屌你老母","createTime":"2020-12-31T04:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T04:14:33.000Z","uid":237538,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"92b91f157723412d47c009dac224a14503b2d882","tid":2347371,"uid":237538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvvubrb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuvvubrb.png&h=817580ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(長文)唔好唔信出軌只有零同無限依句說話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2347172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2347172</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n玩apps一個月食過幾條女 你問我答<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/157854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/157854</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大波你又食，平胸acup你又食，靚嘅你又食，樣衰你都話要頂硬上食埋，你有冇職業操守架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留返啲機會俾其他人好唔好<br />\n你食到咁撚雜都算，但你驗完愛滋又唔講埋陽性定陰性，正常人會唔會無端白事走去驗愛滋呀，鬼唔係你條嘢生粒粒或者邊到乸住痛淆底先去驗咩，咁係咪要各位巴打以後溝咗條女要拎住你張相問下有冇經手過呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幸福賓周浩德 我屌你老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854842944d84c50366ee51584190fb53a02d8130","tid":2347371,"uid":237538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怒推"},{"pid":"2872afa67b3a8ea68fb57283d89804c70464a1d6","tid":2347371,"uid":85751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"姣婆遇著姿粉客"},{"pid":"e664c14260d3d10dccda5aa4f8aa61cbe2a51bc2","tid":2347371,"uid":87507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"你個標題好垃圾，應該係愛滋狗公周浩德"},{"pid":"f6c2f92f039734cc52ddc2996c166ed0d1c1450f","tid":2347371,"uid":162558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset